                "invention-title": [
                    "Hydrogen-alcohol co-production system and method with deep peak regulation unit coupled with oxygen-enriched combustion and carbon capture",
                    "一种深度调峰机组耦合富氧燃烧及碳捕集的氢醇联产系统及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention discloses a hydrogen-alcohol co-production system and a hydrogen-alcohol co-production method for coupling oxygen-enriched combustion and carbon capture of a deep peak regulation unit, electric power is used for electrolyzing water to produce hydrogen, and meanwhile, oxygen generated in the electrolysis process is used for oxygen-enriched combustion, so that the combustion stability of a boiler under low load is improved, and meanwhile, the concentration of carbon dioxide in flue gas is improved. The power generation unit is used for providing electric energy for the water electrolysis unit and generating hydrogen and oxygen at the same time, the oxygen is conveyed into the power generation unit for oxygen-enriched combustion, the generated flue gas is conveyed to the carbon capture and storage unit for capturing and storing carbon dioxide, and finally the carbon dioxide and the hydrogen pass through the alcohol synthesis unit to produce alcohols such as methanol and ethanol. According to the system, carbon dioxide in flue gas generated by the power generation unit can be collected through the carbon capture and storage unit, finally, the carbon dioxide reacts with hydrogen and the like through the alcohol synthesis unit, finally, alcohols are obtained, carbon emission can be reduced, meanwhile, stable combustion of a boiler under low load is guaranteed, and extra economic benefits are brought to a thermal power plant."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明公开了一种深度调峰机组耦合富氧燃烧及碳捕集的氢醇联产系统及方法，采用电力用于电解水制氢，同时电解过程产生的氧气用于富氧燃烧，提高低负荷下锅炉燃烧稳定性，同时提高烟气中二氧化碳浓度。采用发电单元为电解水单元提供电能，同时产生氢气与氧气，氧气输送进发电单元内部进行富氧燃烧，将产生的烟气输送至碳捕集储存单元进行二氧化碳的捕集与储存，最后将二氧化碳与氢气经醇合成单元后生产甲醇、乙醇等醇类。该系统能够将发电单元产生的烟气中的二氧化碳通过碳捕集储存单元进行收集，最后通过醇合成单元将二氧化碳与氢气等进行反应，最终得到醇类，能够降低碳排放的同时，并保证低负荷下锅炉的稳定燃烧，为火电厂带来额外经济收益。"
                }
            ]
